Raspberry Pi alternatives

Hackboard 2: https://www.crowdsupply.com/hackboard/hb2
Dual Core Intel Celeron N4020 CPU
4GB DDR4 RAM
64GB EMMC
2x M.2 slots
Gigabit Ethernet
3x USB 3.0 Type B ports
HDMI
Audio Jack
40 pin Pi compatible GPIO
Wifi and bluetooth

ZimaBoard: mini home server: https://blog.jmdawson.co.uk/zimaboard-a-70-single-board-home-server/ : https://www.zimaboard.com/
Spec	ZimaBoard 216	            ZimaBoard 832
CPU	Intel Celeron N3350	        Intel Celeron N3450
RAM	2GB LPDDR4	                8G LPDDR4
